{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A relaxing vacation, a leisurely journey - that\u2019s how it was supposed to be. However, a brutal storm shattered everything. After the cruise ship wrecked, you washed up on the shores of a mysterious tropical island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here, you\u2019ll find vast beaches, endless coastlines, dense jungles, and wildlife that may not be as harmless as they seem\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660260/extras/background_with_no_logo.jpg?t=1734680504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On this isolated island, you\u2019ll face daunting challenges. Food, water, shelter\u2014everything you need to survive must be gathered or crafted by your own hands. You\u2019ll have to explore the island, forage and hunt for food, hone your skills to craft tools and resources, and maybe even help other survivors escape with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you find a way to survive?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Card-based island survival </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every resource, tool, and action in the game is represented as a card, offering a unique strategy-driven survival experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660260/extras/\u5b64\u5c9b\u6c42\u751f\u52a8\u56feen1.gif?t=1734680504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gather and hunt to survive </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Food and resources are your lifelines. Gather materials or hunt wildlife to make it through each day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660260/extras/\u5b64\u5c9b\u6c42\u751f\u52a8\u56feen2.gif?t=1734680504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meet other survivors </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may not be alone on the island. Encounter other survivors\u2014whether they become allies or foes is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660260/extras/\u4f19\u4f34us.gif?t=1734680504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple endings </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you find a way off the island, or carve out a new life here? The story\u2019s outcome is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face the ultimate test of survival on a remote island, and uncover your own adventure.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Tool","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/6f56f370af7ceac67af5315c2bef4acd13e580f2.jpg"},{"name":"\u5f00\u5929\u8f9f\u5730","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/801751e4c43a4ab5982dff9ed35dec9033216fe9.jpg"},{"name":"Food!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/dcef387e2ccd3f2a4cbe2524dd9c0a8e3687a400.jpg"},{"name":"Cook a Fish","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/8fd724a2ddb252616be2211f0647c2dd56e6b48a.jpg"},{"name":"Roasted Chicken Wings, My Favorite!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/3cbb37d1761704e504d0b0defb2ddc1ec9ef91e0.jpg"},{"name":"Water!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/70d9004f74b9e7be8f4ca082e261a19da303fe7a.jpg"},{"name":"Light!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/2e9ffdfe70397fc2a0721b9d521b12a722fbb3fc.jpg"},{"name":"Something To Shelter Me With...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2660260/be5805afd5cd94c356d6427096d7c75b38762db7.jpg"},{"name":"Give Me A Break...",